@startuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 400
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "Announcement\nMaker" as Maker
actor "Announcement\nChecker" as Checker
participant "MEPS+\n(External System)" as MEPS

box "OMEGA Application Layer" #F0F8FF
participant "OMEGA\nAnnouncement Module" as OMEGA
end box

box "stg Schema" #FFF0F5
database "Staging Tables\n(stg_meps_in_secmast,\nstg_meps_in_secint)" as STG
end box

box "sec Schema" #F5FFFA
database "Security Master\n(sec_security_master)" as SEC_DB
end box

box "iss Schema" #FFFFF0
database "Announcement Master\n(iss_announcement_details)" as ANN_DB
database "Issuance Master\n(iss_issuance)" as ISS_DB
end box

== Phase 1: Announcement Drafting & Approval ==
Maker -> OMEGA : 1. Update Announcement (Draft)
activate OMEGA
OMEGA -> ANN_DB : 2. Save Draft to iss_announcement_details\n(status = 'ISSANNSTAT_DRAFT')

Checker -> OMEGA : 3. Review & Approve
OMEGA -> ANN_DB : 4. Approve Announcement\n(status = 'ISSANNSTAT_PENDING_MEPS')
note right of ANN_DB: **SOURCE OF TRUTH:** iss_announcement_details acts as the absolute source of truth for publication.\nAfter approval/overriding, the previous approved data is stored under the **iss_announcement_details_t** table for audit.
OMEGA --> Checker : 5. Send Email to FD team to create security in MEPS+
deactivate OMEGA

== Phase 2: MEPS+ Integration (secmast.txt) ==
MEPS -> OMEGA : 6. Send secmast.txt
activate OMEGA
OMEGA -> STG : 7. Parse & LOAD into stg_meps_in_secmast

OMEGA -> SEC_DB : 8. INSERT/UPDATE sec_security_master
note right of SEC_DB: **1-TO-MANY:** One sec_security_master record will hold multiple iss_issuance records connected to it (e.g., New = 1, Reopen = 2).

OMEGA -> ISS_DB : 9. INSERT/UPDATE iss_issuance

OMEGA -> OMEGA : 10. Cross-validate values in stg_meps_in_secmast\nagainst iss_announcement_details

alt Validation Passed
    == Phase 3: Verification & Publication ==
    OMEGA -> ISS_DB : 11. UPDATE iss_issuance
    OMEGA -> ANN_DB : 12. UPDATE iss_announcement_details with finalized MEPS+ data\n(status = 'ISSANNSTAT_PENDING_PUBLICATION')
    
    OMEGA -> OMEGA : 13. Scheduled Time Reached
    OMEGA -> ANN_DB : 14. UPDATE iss_announcement_details\n(status = 'ISSANNSTAT_PUBLISHED')
    OMEGA -> OMEGA : 15. Publish Announcement to MAS Website & Retail PDs
    note left of OMEGA: Extracted directly from iss_announcement_details.\n**This published data will NOT be affected by daily secint.txt updates.**
end
deactivate OMEGA

== Phase 4: Daily Securities Update (secint.txt) ==
MEPS -> OMEGA : 16. Send secint.txt (Daily coupon updates)
activate OMEGA
OMEGA -> STG : 17. Parse & LOAD into stg_meps_in_secint

OMEGA -> ISS_DB : 18. UPDATE iss_issuance (Applied ONLY where **issue_no = 1**)
note right of ISS_DB: **DAILY UPDATES & CALCULATIONS:** \nUpdates **ex_int_dt, next_coupon_payment_dt, last_coupon_payment_dt, and int_paid_ind**\nstrictly for the base issuance (issue_no = 1).\n\nFuture calculations for rates/prices will be based on this updated secint data.
deactivate OMEGA
@enduml